OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FGrey and cloudy with outbreaks
OL,6,Fof rain through the morning. Further,
OL,7,Flocally heavy, rain or showers
OL,8,Fpossible during the afternoon. Rain
OL,9,Fand cloud clearing later to deliver a
OL,10,Ffine, sunny evening for most. Winds
OL,11,Fremain blustery throughout.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FPlenty of late sunshine for
OL,14,Fmost under clearing skies, with winds
OL,15,Feasing. One or two light showers
OL,16,Fpossible into the hours of darkness,
OL,17,Fdry and clear after midnight. Chilly.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
