OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FDry and cloudy through the
OL,6,Fmorning. Isolated light rain possible
OL,7,Fthrough the morning, mainly across
OL,8,Fwestern hills. Winds strengthening
OL,9,Flater, strong inland with coastal
OL,10,Fgales into the evening.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FStrong
OL,13,Fwinds and coastal gales easing Sunday
OL,14,Fmorning, followed by scattered
OL,15,Fblustery showers, wintry over higher
OL,16,Fground. Sunshine and light winds
OL,17,FMonday; breezier Tuesday but staying
OL,18,Fdry and sunny.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
